Attendees of the third National Green Growth Conference and Exhibition were hosted to a cocktail reception at the KICC Tsavo Ballroom, Nairobi on Tuesday evening.The event summed up the conference activities where key industry players discussed Kenya s green growth agenda. Top young entrepreneurs with green innovations from various counties were also awarded.The conference was organised by the Micro Enterprises Support Programme Trust in collaboration with the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Denmark (DANIDA) through the Royal Danish Embassy in Kenya.